Cyber Claw:





Cyber Claw returned a cold eye to Injector. "Well I am, a Predacon, they 
must know that." She took flight, a slight pain hitting her shoulder, 
following the groups of Predacons. She heard the name Hell Beast, and 
wondered at his importance with Megatron. He may be a high rank. "Who is 
Hell Beast?" she asked.
